JUDY WOODRUFF: And
I'm Judy Woodruff.

00:08.475 --> 00:12.379 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: On the "NewsHour"
tonight: the immigration divide.
Republican presidential

00:12.379 --> 00:16.950 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
candidates debate what they
would do, and they don't always
agree.

00:16.950 --> 00:21.488 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Also ahead this
Wednesday: another hit for the
companies behind fantasy

00:21.488 --> 00:26.393 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
