what it calls illegal gambling.

00:26.393 --> 00:30.163 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And we travel to the
country of Georgia to stand at
the crossroads of human

00:30.163 --> 00:32.199 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
history.

00:32.199 --> 00:34.902 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK, Fellow, National
Geographic: I think we're
standing on one of the oldest

00:34.902 --> 00:38.872 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
