campus. He had allegedly said he
planned to open fire today

06:17.510 --> 06:20.880 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in Columbia.

06:20.880 --> 06:26.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Earlier this week, protests over
racial tensions led the
university system's president to
resign.

06:26.820 --> 06:30.890 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
