other threats and have stepped
up patrols.

06:30.890 --> 06:37.764 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: A Texas grand jury
has indicted 106 bikers arrested
in last may's deadly gang

06:37.764 --> 06:44.137 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
