another 71 bikers.

06:52.612 --> 06:57.817 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And on Wall
Street, the Dow Jones industrial
average lost 56 points to

06:57.817 --> 07:05.925 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
