07:17.203 --> 07:22.976 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
more.

07:22.976 --> 07:35.889 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Republicans eager to
either hold on to or steal the
spotlight took to the stage

07:35.889 --> 07:42.429 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
