power in the world.

08:34.147 --> 08:42.021 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. RAND PAUL: Yeah, but,
Marco, Marco, how is it
conservative, how is it
conservative

08:42.021 --> 08:44.424 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
to add a trillion-dollar
expenditure for the federal
government that you're not
paying

08:44.424 --> 08:46.159 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
for?

08:46.159 --> 08:49.662 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate: We have to get smart.
We can't continue to

08:49.662 --> 08:52.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
