08:52.866 --> 08:57.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEB BUSH (R), Presidential
Candidate: Donald's wrong on
this. He is absolutely wrong on
this.

08:57.070 --> 09:01.307 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
