world's policeman, but we sure
as heck better be the world's

09:01.307 --> 09:03.042 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
leader.

09:03.042 --> 09:07.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And they targeted
the Democrat they clearly expect
to face next year.

09:07.847 --> 09:11.351 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CARLY FIORINA (R), Presidential
Candidate: We must beat Hillary
Clinton. Carly Fiorina

09:11.351 --> 09:14.788 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
can beat Hillary Clinton. I
will beat Hillary Clinton.

09:14.788 --> 09:18.892 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: But the biggest
chasm of policy difference was
immigration. Trump once again

09:18.892 --> 09:22.395 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
