between the U.S. and Mexico, and
deporting 11 million immigrants

09:22.395 --> 09:24.731 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in the country illegally.

09:24.731 --> 09:28.301 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: Dwight Eisenhower,
good president, great president,
moved a 1.5 million illegal

09:28.301 --> 09:33.840 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
