back. They moved a 1.5 million
people out. We have no

09:38.445 --> 09:39.412 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
choice.

09:39.412 --> 09:42.282 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: But others
on stage objected.

09:42.282 --> 09:46.686 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GOV. JOHN KASICH (R-OH),
Presidential Candidate: But for
the 11 million people, come on,
folks.

09:46.686 --> 09:51.925 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
