not an adult argument.

09:55.728 --> 09:59.032 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEB BUSH: It's not embracing
American values. And it would
tear communities apart. And it

09:59.032 --> 10:01.601 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
