not the kind of country that I
know America is.

10:01.601 --> 10:04.037 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

10:04.037 --> 10:07.941 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Bush and Kasich
didn't say what they would do
instead, but Ted Cruz said
anything

10:07.941 --> 10:10.844 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
