would hurt the country.

10:10.844 --> 10:14.747 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SEN. TED CRUZ (R-TX),
Presidential Candidate: If
Republicans join Democrats as
the party

10:14.747 --> 10:17.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of amnesty, we will lose. I
understand that when the
mainstream media covers
immigration,

10:17.951 --> 10:21.421 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
