economic issue. But I can tell
you, for millions of Americans

10:21.421 --> 10:24.257 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
at home watching this, it is a
very personal economic issue.

10:24.257 --> 10:27.193 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Rubio stayed out of
last night's fray, but weighed
in this morning on the Obama

10:27.193 --> 10:30.163 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
