DACA that would delay
deportation proceedings for
undocumented

10:30.163 --> 10:33.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
immigrants whose children
were born in the U.S.

10:33.566 --> 10:39.138 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCO RUBIO: I do not support
DACA. It's unconstitutional;
it's the wrong way to do this,
and, quite

10:39.138 --> 10:41.307 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
