enforce our immigration laws in
this country or we don't have
immigration

10:41.307 --> 10:43.142 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
laws.

10:43.142 --> 10:46.379 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Economics and the
politics of immigration are
expected to remain front and

10:46.379 --> 10:48.081 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
center throughout
the campaign year.

