Immigrant Justice Fund, and Josh

10:54.587 --> 10:57.991 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Blackman, an associate professor
at the South Texas College of
Law.

10:57.991 --> 11:01.895 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Marielena Hincapie, let me ask
-- start by asking you what
leaped out at you in watching

11:01.895 --> 11:05.765 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
