part, the immigration debate
last night?

11:05.765 --> 11:08.301 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARIELENA HINCAPIE, Executive
Director, National Immigration
Law Center: Thank you, Gwen.

11:08.301 --> 11:13.039 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I, frankly, was initially
shocked at what I was starting
to hear from Trump, and then

11:13.039 --> 11:18.411 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
deeply, deeply troubled. It was
surreal. I think many viewers
may not realize that when

11:18.411 --> 11:23.883 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
