25:52.684 --> 25:55.120 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID LORDKIPANIDZE, Director,
Georgia National Museum: What we
found here, it changed our

25:55.120 --> 26:04.430 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
