28:17.963 --> 28:20.499 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN:
Taking care of others.

28:20.499 --> 28:23.035 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
How did these guys get to
