issues. Slavery is in the story.

40:53.251 --> 40:59.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: And just
what it was like in England
after slavery has been
abolished,

40:59.490 --> 41:05.897 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and how people relate to the
colonies, because every time you
see Victorian England depicted,

41:05.897 --> 41:09.734 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
