halftime, he had -- he smoked
cigarettes.

43:02.847 --> 43:04.916 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes.

43:04.916 --> 43:08.186 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: And I
overheard the ball boys talking
about it one time. They said

43:08.186 --> 43:13.825 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
they don't like going into the
shower room because Bob had been
in there smoking cigarettes.

43:13.825 --> 43:18.362 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I realized that, if Bob
smoked cigarettes at halftime,
if I could get him to run a lot

43:18.362 --> 43:20.431 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
in the second half,
he would be in pain.

43:20.431 --> 43:21.332 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

43:21.332 --> 43:23.835 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: That was
your Sherlock moment.

43:23.835 --> 43:27.772 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: Yes, and I
would gain an advantage at that
point.

43:27.772 --> 43:32.510 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, things like that, I would
just try to pay attention to
what's going on and use my

43:32.510 --> 43:38.816 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
powers of observation. But, you
know, Sherlock is much more in
depth because of all the
different

43:38.816 --> 43:45.690 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
facts that he can correlate.
He's into so many arcane bits of
knowledge that help him

43:45.690 --> 43:49.827 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
see things. I always describe it
as Sherlock sees in technicolor
and we see everything

43:49.827 --> 43:52.230 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in black and white.

43:52.230 --> 43:55.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: I saw you play so
many times. I saw you destroy my
team, the Celtics, many

43:55.766 --> 43:56.267 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
times.

43:56.267 --> 43:58.002 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

43:58.002 --> 44:03.174 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: I never imagined
that Sherlock was -- Sherlock
Holmes was somehow playing

44:03.174 --> 44:05.243 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
into all that.

44:05.243 --> 44:11.949 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: Well, just
for anyone who has to figure out
things, if they read

44:11.949 --> 44:15.720 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Arthur Conan Doyle, they will
get an idea about how keen your
powers of observation

44:15.720 --> 44:18.055 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
