44:18.055 --> 44:21.626 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: You are
publishing books. You're writing
a column for "TIME" magazine.
There's

44:21.626 --> 44:25.162 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
