44:25.162 --> 44:29.834 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You also, earlier this year, had
-- it was quadruple coronary
bypass surgery. Right?

44:29.834 --> 44:30.868 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR:
Yes, scary time.

44:30.868 --> 44:31.769 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Scary time.

44:31.769 --> 44:32.503 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: Yes.

44:32.503 --> 44:35.106 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Sort of a
real brush with mortality.

44:35.106 --> 44:38.643 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: A very
close brush with mortality.

44:38.643 --> 44:45.950 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I had massive blockages that
I wasn't aware of. I only became
aware of it when I

44:45.950 --> 44:50.688 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
