my chest, and I knew something

44:50.688 --> 44:55.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
was up. But I still postponed
going to see the cardiologist
for a couple of months.

44:55.226 --> 44:57.795 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: I suppose that's
hard for a man who's been an
athlete all his life and

44:57.795 --> 45:00.364 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
