45:22.086 --> 45:24.188 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: What a day.

45:24.188 --> 45:25.790 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Happy
birthday, right. Wow.

45:25.790 --> 45:28.893 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR: Yes.

45:28.893 --> 45:35.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right, Kareem
Abdul-Jabbar, thank you for
talking with us.

45:35.266 --> 45:39.670 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR:
It was a pleasure.

45:39.670 --> 45:45.176 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: On the day when
