children. And I think it gives
people a chance to say, we're

48:26.704 --> 48:31.208 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
here for you. Thank you.

48:31.208 --> 48:38.582 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
DENNIS KELLOGG: As these
