to photos of their loved ones.
The Williams are creating

49:27.364 --> 49:32.036 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
similar displays remembering
the fallen from each state.

49:32.036 --> 49:36.006 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
