his mom wrote that's posted next
to his dad's photo.

49:36.006 --> 49:39.844 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WYATT ROBINSON: "Josh, so proud
of you and thank you for all
your memories. Kody and

49:39.844 --> 49:49.954 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
