story alive. Your wife, Rhonda."

49:49.954 --> 49:58.062 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DENNIS KELLOGG: It's just a
short walk from the quiet of the
photo display to the noisy

49:58.062 --> 50:02.032 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
