50:31.829 --> 50:36.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KODY ROBINSON: "Miss you. Love
you. Want you. Your son, always,
Kody. XO, XO."

50:36.533 --> 50:38.435 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RHONDA ROBINSON: "Your memory
will always live strong through
your little girl. Always

50:38.435 --> 50:38.936 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
